'''Darth Sion's starship''' was a warship used by [[Darth Sion]] in [[3951 BBY]]. The ship was found adrift in space near the [[Peragus asteroid field]] in the [[Peragus system/Legends|Peragus system]] by the crew of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] [[Hammerhead-class cruiser|''Hammerhead''-class cruiser]] [[Harbinger (Hammerhead-class)|''Harbinger'']], while ''en route'' to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Telos IV]] on orders of highest priority from [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Carth Onasi]] to ferry a [[Meetra Surik|woman]] there, The ''Harbinger'' sent a boarding party to investigate the ship and found a comatose Sion, immediately sending him to the medical bay and into a [[Kolto/Legends|kolto]] tank. He subsequently escaped and killed everyone on board the Republic ship, taking control of it and used it to reach the [[Peragus Mining Facility]] where the woman he was searching for, Meetra Surik, had been jettisoned to.

